title: Spiders-Man Infests NYCC 2025

author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
This week on the show, we revisit Marvel Studios’ Werewolf by Night as we hear from the director Michael Giacchino, and stars Gael García Bernal and Laura Donnelly. Plus, we continue our journey through the Marvel occult with a comic book breakdown on Ted Sallis aka the Man-Thing! All time codes are approximate.

00:00 - Welcome Back!
1:08 - Director Michael Giacchino, and stars Gael García Bernal and Laura Donnelly talk Werewolf by Night
22:47 - Comic book spotlight: Man-Thing (Ted Sallis)
